{"TopicId":135701,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Starting in KSP v1.2 mods will no longer be supported","CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T18:31:49Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T18:31:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I just saw an official thread posted in the Steam forums, that with all the new changes due to Unity, and that the console versions of KSP cant support mods, Squad will be locking up the KSP API starting in v1.2, and bringing the PC version more inline with the console builds, so that mods will no longer be supported. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:0.0:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:0.0:\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nKSP will then be \u0022Play vanilla...or Go Home!\u0022\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nEDIT: Yes, now that its April 2nd, this WAS a lame attempt at an April Fools joke... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-02T20:50:15Z\u0022 title=\u002204/02/2016 08:50  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 2, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Stone Blue\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CobaltWolf","CreatedById":105588,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T18:35:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nK.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T18:51:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems #legit\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Randazzo","CreatedById":136468,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T18:55:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat if I\u0027m already home?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Motokid600","CreatedById":66349,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T19:01:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI hate April 1st\u00A0so much...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T19:45:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat, KSP will lose all of its buyers and SQUAD will become what it was, all over again. How lovely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T19:56:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222488333\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135701\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459539902\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135127\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Matuchkin\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Matuchkin said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat, KSP will lose all of its buyers and SQUAD will become what it was, all over again. How lovely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah... It will become Game of the Year, as the next big Facebook/MySpace game... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T20:01:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222488363\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135701\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221459540589\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002277721\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Stone Blue\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, Stone Blue said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah... It will become Game of the Year, as the next big Facebook/MySpace game... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWithout mods, the game will remain with the small amount of limited-use parts it currently has. It won\u0027t have any extra utilities, such as a twr or Dv readout. There will be no way to make it an actual simulator, with RO, and players will be confined on a tiny solar system with no realism whatsoever.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt will be unplayable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-01T20:02:42Z\u0022 title=\u002204/01/2016 08:02  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 1, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Matuchkin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FreeThinker","CreatedById":117389,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T20:26:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI will be content with a 1.1 version. At least now we get some stability. And in the Mean time, Squad can work on their Sequel.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"lextacy","CreatedById":107955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T20:29:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAPRIL PHOOOOLS !!!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Azimech","CreatedById":50750,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-01T21:58:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA very late joke, it is. But nice.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"FrancoisH","CreatedById":124888,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-02T00:34:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just read that, I laughed a little and thought... This game would be dead... Look at their team, they hired people amongst mods creator, would be just impossible to do that and survive. So I finally thought it wasn\u0027t that a funny joke to make! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:angry:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_angry.png\u0022 title=\u0022:angry:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeems on the line with the Google one...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022KMzwG_f-maxage-0.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://m.popkey.co/fba93c/KMzwG_f-maxage-0.gif\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...joking\u00A0as well \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-02T00:35:54Z\u0022 title=\u002204/02/2016 12:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 2, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by FrancoisH\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Skybird0","CreatedById":161024,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-02T20:37:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYikes... That is... scary...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-02T20:49:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, now that its April 2nd, this was a lame attempt at an April Fools joke... \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003